00:05:34,190 --> 00:05:37,118

126
00:05:37,118 --> 00:05:39,374
OK?

127
00:05:39,374 --> 00:05:40,540
So, let's put this together.

128
00:05:40,540 --> 00:05:41,970
Imagine we take
a charged sphere,

129
00:05:41,970 --> 00:05:43,928
