146
00:06:15,829 --> 00:06:18,370
The thing you get by ripping a
negative charge off a hydrogen

147
00:06:18,370 --> 00:06:18,930
atom.

148
00:06:18,930 --> 00:06:20,070
So, take your
electron and send it

149
00:06:20,070 --> 00:06:21,130
