1077
00:47:48,964 --> 00:47:56,790
So, u of r must go
to 0 at r goes to 0.

1078
00:47:56,790 --> 00:47:59,330

1079
00:47:59,330 --> 00:48:02,060
Because if it goes to a
constant-- any constant--

1080
00:48:02,060 --> 00:48:06,545
we've got a bad divergence
