1081
00:48:06,545 --> 00:48:08,390
In particular, if we
calculate the energy,

1082
00:48:08,390 --> 00:48:12,254
we'll discover that the
energy is badly divergent.

1083
00:48:12,254 --> 00:48:17,650
It does become divergent if
